templates.name: ClassList $liste (prefLabelFr séparées par des virgules) lac,nappe d'eau,point d'eau,réservoir,autre cours d'eau,rivière,ruisseau
templates.cypher:
match (c:ClassOOR) where c.prefLabelFr in split($liste,",")
return c

templates.name: ClassOOR avec plusieurs type de geom
templates.cypher: match (c:ClassOOR) where exists(c.hasInstanceInLayer) and size(c.hasInstanceInLayer)>1 return c

templates.name: ClassSelection non feuilles
templates.cypher:
match (c:ClassSelection )<-[r]-(c1:ClassSelection)
where not exists((:ClassSelection )-[r]->(c1:ClassSelection) )
return c,r

templates.name: shortestPath between ClassOOR $prefLabelFr1 and $prefLabelFr2
templates.cypher:
match p=shortestPath((c1:ClassOOR)-[*0..10]-(c2:ClassOOR))
where c1.prefLabelFr = $prefLabelFr1 and  c2.prefLabelFr = $prefLabelFr2 
AND ALL(x IN nodes(p)[1..-1] WHERE x:ClassOOR  )
RETURN p

templates.name: instanciated ClassOOR
templates.cypher: match (c1:ClassOOR)<-[r2:isSubClassOf|isAltLabelOf]-(c2:ClassOOR) where c1.instancesDirectes > 1 or c1.instancesCumulees >1 return c1,c2,r2

templates.name: ClassOOR and AltLabelFr with same name
templates.text: ClassOOR and AltLabelFr with same name

templates.name: OOR classes avec plusieurs parents
templates.cypher: match (c:ClassOOR)-[r:isSubClassOf]->(c1:ClassOOR) with  c as class, count(r) as count , collect(r) as rels, collect(c1) as parents where count >1 return class,rels, parents

templates.name: objets $class nom contenant $string
templates.cypher: match (:ClassOOR {prefLabelFr:$class})-[:isInstanceOf]-(o:ObjetGeo) where toLower(o.name) contains $name return o;
